@startuml
title BidMart Future Context Diagram After Risk Storming
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Buyer/User" as Buyer <<User>>
actor "Seller/User" as Seller <<User>>
actor "Admin" as Admin <<User>>

component "BidMart Auth/Core Interfaces" as UserClients <<Frontend>>
component "BidMart Admin Interface" as AdminClient <<Frontend>>
component "BidMart Platform Boundary\nAuth service + Core service + Admin service" as Platform <<System>>
cloud "Email Provider" as Email <<External System>>
component "Monitoring / Logging" as Obs <<External System>>

Buyer --> UserClients : uses BidMart
Seller --> UserClients : uses BidMart
Admin --> AdminClient : uses admin interface
UserClients --> Platform : HTTPS through gateway
AdminClient --> Platform : HTTPS through gateway
Platform --> Email : async verification,\npassword reset, MFA email
Platform --> Obs : metrics, traces,\nlogs, alerts
@enduml
